@page
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
<p><em>Last updated: June 2026</em></p>

<h3>Data We Collect</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Email address (for account creation and authentication)</li>
    <li>Session identifiers (managed by ASP.NET Core Identity)</li>
    <li>Approximate location from stop confirmations (only when you voluntarily report)</li>
    <li>Push subscription tokens (if you opt in to notifications)</li>
</ul>

<h3>How Data Is Used</h3>
<ul>
    <li>To authenticate you and maintain your session</li>
    <li>To provide personalised transit predictions and grid alerts</li>
    <li>To send push notifications and digest emails (if opted in)</li>
    <li>To improve prediction accuracy using anonymised crowdsourced reports</li>
</ul>

<h3>Data Retention</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Account data is retained until you delete your account</li>
    <li>Anonymous transit report data is retained for 90 days</li>
    <li>Grid readings are retained for 90 days</li>
</ul>

<h3>Third-Party Processors</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Google Maps (Alphabet Inc.)</strong> — used to display stop locations. Subject to Google's Privacy Policy.</li>
    <li><strong>SMTP provider</strong> — if email notifications are configured, your email address is processed by the configured SMTP service.</li>
    <li><strong>National Transport Authority (NTA)</strong> — transit data is sourced from the NTA GTFS-R feeds.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Your GDPR Rights</h3>
<p>Under GDPR you have the right to:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Access</strong> — request a copy of your personal data</li>
    <li><strong>Rectification</strong> — correct inaccurate data</li>
    <li><strong>Erasure</strong> — request deletion of your account and associated data</li>
    <li><strong>Portability</strong> — receive your data in a machine-readable format</li>
    <li><strong>Objection</strong> — object to processing of your data</li>
</ul>
<p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:admin@yourdomain.ie">admin@yourdomain.ie</a>.</p>

<h3>No Data Sold</h3>
<p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties for advertising purposes.</p>
